premise_source_doc_sentence: Despite generally mixed reviews from critics , the film grossed $ 112.5 million in the United States and $ 215.4 million worldwide , becoming the eighth-highest-grossing film of 1989 .
It received a positive response from critics and audiences and grossed $ 242 million in the United States and more than $ 295 million worldwide .
The film grossed $ 229 million worldwide against a production budget of $ 144 million .
Ghostbusters II is a 1990 video game for the NES , developed by Imagineering and published by Activision , based on the film Ghostbusters II .
In Europe and Japan , HAL Laboratory released its own Ghostbusters II game called New Ghostbusters II .
